* {{ill|Prince Shōtoku|ja|聖徳太子}}
* {{ill|Emperor Yōmei|ja|用明天皇}}
* {{ill|Empress Suiko|ja|推古天皇}}
* {{ill|Prince Ameoshitarashi|ja|天足彦国押人命}}

== External Links ==
* [http://www.asahi-net.or.jp/~eh6k-ymgs/book/furuta/zuisho.htm ''Sui Shu Wa State Account'' (archived)]
* [http://www.geocities.jp/intelljp/cn-history/zui/wa.htm ''Sui Shu'' Vol. 81, East Yi, Wa State (archived)]

